　　滷船鹽<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>　滷船運滷入團鹽<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>載鹽上倉滷船<lb/>
　　其身淺易於牽運鹽<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>上有摧槽橄板鎖封闗防<lb/>
　　船艕<hi>艕同榜竝船也</hi>官為印烙<lb/>
大<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>
                    <hi>
                        <graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>音貂吴船也</hi>小<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>名雖共鹽<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>滷船各適用滷船淺淺<lb/>
搆作艙鹽<graphic n="KR0657" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0657.png" mimeType="image/png"/>實實装其<graphic n="KR1299" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1299.png" mimeType="image/png"/>
                    <hi>
                        <graphic n="KR1299" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1299.png" mimeType="image/png"/>音洞博雅舟名</hi>灰滷附團便且輕<lb/>
鹽鹺到倉逺而重也無橈槳與風㠶篾纜牛牽運防送<lb/>
