<pb n="KR2m0045_WYG_002-26b"/>
　　塌車<graphic n="KR0008" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0008.png" mimeType="image/png"/>車　運柴必用<graphic n="KR0008" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0008.png" mimeType="image/png"/>
                    <hi>
                        <graphic n="KR0008" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0008.png" mimeType="image/png"/>字字書韻書俱不載未詳</hi>車塌車<lb/>
　　二車大小各隨其製皆用樟榆等硬木做造方可<lb/>
　　耐久管車輪軸頭處每輛用生鐵鑄成鐵管四箇<lb/>
　　穿套在車機内籠軸其中庶耐轉軸名曰團穿有<lb/>
　　力之家則造<graphic n="KR0008" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0008.png" mimeType="image/png"/>車無力之家用塌車盖<graphic n="KR0008" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0008.png" mimeType="image/png"/>車用費<lb/>
　　牛力倍於塌車數倍故也<lb/>
千牛宻攢蹄車聲雷長堤擔夫欲争道長驅與之齊束<lb/>
草如山髙牧子猶嫌低陸地行尚可可憐行深泥<lb/>
<pb n="KR2m0045_WYG_002-27a"/>
</p>
